      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It sounds like you are going through a profound and agonizing pain right now, feeling completely abandoned and hopeless. Please know that these intense feelings, while overwhelming, are not permanent, even if they feel that way. Reaching out to a crisis hotline or mental health professional can provide immediate support during this incredibly dark time. You do not have to carry this crushing weight all by yourself.",
